node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Entrepreneurship | Business on August 24, 2021 tagging @bastiaanslot_. May be an image of text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 7 principles that made me a millionaire in my early 20s. (A thread)'.

Photo shared by Entrepreneurship | Business on August 24, 2021 tagging @bastiaanslot_. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot Goal setting. If you don't know what you want, then you don't know what to do. Set one clear tangible goal. Achieve your goal, then repeat.'.

Photo shared by Entrepreneurship | Business on August 24, 2021 tagging @bastiaanslot_. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 2. Sacrifice. If you don't sacrifice for what you want, then your goal becomes the sacrifice.'.

Photo shared by Entrepreneurship | Business on August 24, 2021 tagging @bastiaanslot_. May be an image of text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 3. Health. Sleep well Eat healthy. Meditate. Exercise. Take time to relax. If you aren't performing at your best, your business won't either.'.

Photo shared by Entrepreneurship | Business on August 24, 2021 tagging @bastiaanslot_. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 4. Gratitude. Always looking to the future can cause fear, anxiety, and stress. Practice gratitude daily to balance yourself.'.

Photo shared by Entrepreneurship | Business on August 24, 2021 tagging @bastiaanslot_. May be an image of text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 5. Resist impulses. When you're working, resist all urges to eat snacks, grab a treat, or check social media. Train yourself to stay focused on the task at hand, and don't let anything distract you that's how you make progress.'.

Photo shared by Entrepreneurship | Business on August 24, 2021 tagging @bastiaanslot_. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 6. Consistency. Whether you're seeing great results or no results at all, you need to stay consistent. Stay consistent without expecting immediate results. It will all add up long term.'.

Photo shared by Entrepreneurship | Business on August 24, 2021 tagging @bastiaanslot_. May be an image of text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot 7. Invest in yourself. etc. Whether it's books, mentors, seminars, Make sure you're constantly investing in your own growth. You don't have to figure out everything on your own. Find someone who has the results you want and learn from them. That's your "shortcut" to success.'.

Photo shared by Entrepreneurship | Business on August 24, 2021 tagging @bastiaanslot_. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'Bastiaan Slot @_bastiaanslot Whenever you're feeling stuck or like you're not making progress in life you can always go back to these principles and see where you're goino wrong. focus on these daily to make sure I stay on track.'.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Entrepreneurship | Business on August 22, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'You wake up without an alarm. You are in no rush. You plan out your day No traffic You work on your own terms. You can take a break at any time. Read or exercise when you want to. That's financial freedom. THEBUSINESSHACKS'.

node.text:
Having the freedom to work on your own terms and working on things you are passionate about is the goal.
-
However, working for yourself is not as simple as you might think.
-
You need to figure out what you need to do to grow your business.
-
You need discipline and hold yourself accountable.
-
But if you make it happen it's one of the most rewarding things.
-
Follow @thebusinesshacks for more.
